data.description: Charming 3 BD/2 BA home in convenient location! Beautiful laminate wood flooring in main areas, vaulted ceilings, dual pane windows. Spacious kitchen with oak cabinets offering ample storage space, Stove and Water Heater approx. 1 yr old. Both Bathrooms have been tastefully updated. Covered patio, inviting outdoor space to enjoy.
